{"tid":1106614,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"csl 未完約 但轉 同台其他plan？","createTime":"2019-04-14T16:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T15:10:31.000Z","uid":81202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"423e0c4ee452da64e446b11c32fb69440b4df276","tid":1106614,"uid":81202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"csl<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過未完約<br />\n又去門市轉同台既其他plan？<br />\n<br />\n事關之前有sales sell 我 csl 298+18  三年約<br />\n第一年免費，之後收正價<br />\n所以 total 係 ( 298+18 ) * 24 / 36 = 211$<br />\n<br />\n之後佢又話，如果係一年後，轉出機plan<br />\n以iphone 為例<br />\n408$ + 機價，就可以做到月費：<br />\n(408 * 24 + 機價) / 36 =  150＄ 個月<br />\n<br />\n而家就黎完一年，去門市問轉plan 詳情<br />\n佢話我呢個係續約，要轉出比原來plan 貴<br />\n即係548+18 有6+ 6GB data<br />\n<br />\n我追問點解唔可以 408 + 18<br />\n佢話 408 可能包左機價，機佔200，咁個plan 值200，所以比原先平。<br />\n<br />\n我無追問，但而家諗番起覺得好可笑。邊個黎定義408plan？<br />\n<br />\n有個巴打有相同經歷可以分享？<br />\n當年與sales 對話有錄音及紀錄清楚日期、時間<br />\n唔排除告上消委會。"},{"pid":"a678145457c1d21f57f3c0bd9896e26c2fac4e4a","tid":1106614,"uid":176640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1a5d182f1a3500d421d72151e2a7fa6fabaae39","tid":1106614,"uid":178101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a46593c2073aed68d9fb80b7febffa18f34b1d2","tid":1106614,"uid":188145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7c655242f9bcec55c202487001fbfb9e6afe9b3","tid":1106614,"uid":117267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abcf487ffcfcee4f675a8b05f2470005ab1c0e2a","tid":1106614,"uid":177821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7303cd966a94f9e875ad6ab5a228f386c4c2778","tid":1106614,"uid":237794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:33:23.000Z","ms